## Overview
Enhance the existing time tracking system with professional reporting, billable hours tracking, and analytics. Transform basic time entry into a full-featured time tracking solution competitive with Toggl, Clockify, and Harvest.

## Problem Statement
Current time tracking is functional but lacks:
- **Visual reports** - No charts or trend visualization
- **Billable hours** - Cannot mark time as billable/non-billable
- **Analytics** - No insights into time usage patterns
- **Export capabilities** - Cannot export to CSV/invoice format
- **Project summaries** - No rolled-up project/client totals

**User Value:**
- HIGH for freelancers and consultants (billable tracking)
- MEDIUM for knowledge workers (productivity insights)
- Competitive with paid tools (Toggl $108+/year, Harvest $144+/year)

