## Research Notes

### Toggl Track
- **Standout Feature:** One-click timer with project suggestions
- **Reports:** Weekly/monthly summaries, project breakdowns
- **Export:** CSV, PDF, Excel formats
- **Pricing:** $10/user/month (annual)

### Clockify
- **Standout Feature:** Unlimited users on free tier
- **Reports:** Detailed reports with filtering
- **Calendar View:** Visual time representation
- **Pricing:** Free (basic), $5.99/user/month (pro)

### Harvest
- **Standout Feature:** Invoicing integration
- **Reports:** Profitability analysis, project budgets
- **Team Features:** Time approval workflows
- **Pricing:** $12/user/month (annual)

### Key Insights
- All competitors prioritize **quick entry** (running timer)
- **Visual reports** are table stakes (charts required)
- **Billable tracking** is essential for freelancers
- **Export to CSV** is the minimum (invoicing is advanced)
- **Project budgets** help prevent overages

